<h3 id='event-updates'>Event Updates</h3><pre class="highlight sh tab-shell"><code>curl -X PUT https://collection-prod.inspcdn.net/event <span class="se">\</span>
    -H <span class="s2">"Authorization: Bearer </span><span class="nv">$API_KEY</span><span class="s2">"</span> <span class="se">\</span>
    -d <span class="s1">'{
        "id":          "12345",
        "name":        "Reveillon 2021",
        "dates":  [
            {
                "id":       "1",
                "datetime": 1594210000
            },
            {
                "id":       "2",
                "datetime": 1594315000
            }
        ],
        "description": "We have postponed until next year",
        "slug":        "/reveillon_2021"
    }'</span>
</code></pre>
<p>Send information to Inspetor every time an event listing&#39;s information is updated (event title, location, etc.)</p>
